site_title: Shuttle Dart by Michael G. LaFosse

block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: This is Paper Plane 31 of our 100 Exotic Paper Airplane Challenge. It is the “Shuttle Dart" designed by Michael G. LaFosse. The fuselage of this origami plane is tied together with a lock giving this aircraft great stability. This is an origami plane folded from a square sheet. Enjoy!!! If you missed my last Exotic Paper Airplane "Paper Plane 30 : Ready To Land by Didier Boursin", you could watch it at https://youtu.be/8J-5kVEFqbY Thanks For Watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
